{"tid":1526591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵青衣站有人噴黑及破壞入閘機","createTime":"2019-09-01T06:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T10:56:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":614,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"653ea2ba7e2d86131fd98ce99632c27f28ff9715","tid":1526591,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/01/KPh65b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F01%2FKPh65b.jpg&h=1814268c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n數十人下午到港鐵青衣站內，破壞閉路電視鏡頭、購票機及閘機，並於機件上噴漆。<br />\n<br />\n他們一度離開青衣站，其後部分人折返站內，再次破壞閉路電視鏡頭及噴漆，在場有人撐起雨傘。<br />\n<br />\n現場所見，港鐵職員並無阻止。有市民嘗試拍卡入閘，但不成功。另外亦有人沒有拍卡，跨過閘機，走進月台範圍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478155-20190901.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478155-20190901.htm&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=71595061\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478155-20190901.htm&h=28b3e2a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478155-20190901.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cf266cb7bab7e784070e269e6babe6bd085376d0","tid":1526591,"uid":263058,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:30:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"155ad108e2e287d6067514e84b12f7e1e38c44cb","tid":1526591,"uid":156936,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:32:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做得好</span></span>"},{"pid":"1d8a8354b7f3ad0d31dcd5af26b61ab171976bc1","tid":1526591,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces